{"tid":631615,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一星期的第一天是星期幾？","createTime":"2018-04-16T15:19:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T01:45:07.000Z","uid":70650,"like":86,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bd379e81a75516e87ebaa973f0ff5ac826a87a34","tid":631615,"uid":70650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T15:19:59.000Z","msg":"話說啱啱同朋友傾偈<br />\n佢話今日月尾嘅星期日有嘢做<br />\n之後我問係嘅係下個禮拜日<br />\n佢話係下下禮拜日先啱<br />\n跟住佢話一星期嘅第一日係星期日<br />\n我就話係星期一先啱<br />\n咁到底係星期幾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正評:星期日<br />\n負評:星期一"},{"pid":"7c635703cc0fbc6dc15cd0172b84ba820dae1a1a","tid":631615,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T15:24:42.000Z","msg":"根據聖經，上帝花了六天的時間創造了世界，而在第七天，也就是安息日（星期六）休息了，這一天就被視為慶祝和休息之日，這就使得星期日成了一個星期中的第一天。"},{"pid":"ee5a1d913845301e2d5c654f4f3c61cc5eb486a3","tid":631615,"uid":21873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T15:26:17.000Z","msg":"小學幾年班..."},{"pid":"5a910fc9583473e0f9209607a6dcd6dcdfef1022","tid":631615,"uid":70650,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T15:28:03.000Z","msg":"在許多英語國家、以色列、日本、香港和澳門，一般認爲一个星期開始於星期日。 埃及人的一星期是從星期六開始的。 多數歐洲國家都以星期日為一星期的第一天。 國際標准化組織（ISO 8601）規定星期一爲每星期的第一天"},{"pid":"c7af38f1322ee7f10c1e5aca35e19870f4449947","tid":631615,"uid":24457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T15:29:11.000Z","msg":"你睇下個月曆每個禮拜最頭嗰日係星期幾啦"},{"pid":"3a199552ee4cd48678d4efa1601dbfb61c3954a9","tid":631615,"uid":128325,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T15:29:24.000Z","msg":"竟然咁少人投星期一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4f8771de9975b733c8f6d2ec8eb80dc763f2a09","tid":631615,"uid":70650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c7af38f1322ee7f10c1e5aca35e19870f4449947","tid":631615,"uid":24457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cit